selrach.bnetbuilder.model.distributions.interfaces
Interface UnconditionalDistribution

All Superinterfaces:
ConditionalDistribution
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractUnconditionalDistribution, Gaussian, Sigmoid, Table
public interface UnconditionalDistribution
extends ConditionalDistribution

This is a distribution that has no parents. This is just a special implementation of a conditional distribution with no parents, as such it can have a couple more functions.

Author:
Charles Robertson
